{
    "T04sanss05u:0": " śīlapāramitāyām anarthavarjanaṃ pañcamaḥ paricchedaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:1": " uktaḥ saṃkṣepato 'narthaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:2": " tasya vivarjanaṃ yathâdhyaśayasaṃcodanasūtre /",
    "T04sanss05u:3": " evaṃvidhânarthaśravaṇabhayabhīrukaiḥ",
    "T04sanss05u:4": " [ Cambridge MS f54a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:5": " ādikarmikabodhisatvaiḥ samādānāni yathā gṛhītāni tathā kāryaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:6": " evaṃ-",
    "T04sanss05u:7": " [ Bendall ed p98 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:8": " hi tair uktaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:9": " ete vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa tathāgatasya purataḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:10": " evaṃ samādānaṃ kurmaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:11": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa bodhisatvayānikaṃ pudgalaṃ gṛhiṇaṃ vā pravrajitaṃ",
    "T04sanss05u:12": " vâpattyā codayiṣyāmo bhūtena vâbhūtena vā visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato 'rhan samyaksaṃbuddho bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:13": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa bodhisatvayānikaṃ pudgalam avamanyemâvarṇaṃ câsya bhāṣema visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhaved arhan samyaksaṃbuddhaḥ",
    "T04sanss05u:14": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa bodhisatvayānikaṃ pudgalaṃ gṛhiṇaṃ vā pravrajitaṃ",
    "T04sanss05u:15": " vā pañcabhiḥ kāmaguṇaiḥ krīḍantaṃ paricārayantaṃ daṣṭvâprasādaṃ kuryāma vilekhaṃ",
    "T04sanss05u:16": " vā cittasyôtpādayemâgauravaṃ vôtpādayema na ca tatra śāstṛsaṃjñām utpādayema /",
    "T04sanss05u:17": " visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:18": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa mitrakulabhikṣād akulanidānaṃ bodhisatvayānikānāṃ pudgalānāṃ kāyapīḍāṃ cittapīḍāṃ vā kuryāma visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:19": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa bodhisatvayānikaṃ pudgalaṃ dṛṣṭvâikenâpy amanojñavacanenâbhāṣema visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:20": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa triskṛtvo rātreḥ triskṛtvo divasya bodhisatvayānikaṃ pudgalaṃ na namasyema visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet",
    "T04sanss05u:21": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇâsya vratasamādānasya kṛtaśo rājyapratilambhaṃ vā dhanapratilambhaṃ vā kāyajīvitaṃ vā na parityajema",
    "T04sanss05u:22": " [ Cambridge MS f54b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:23": " visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:24": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa śrāvakayānikaṃ vā pratyekabuddhayānikaṃ vā pudgalam avamanyema /",
    "T04sanss05u:25": " vayaṃ viśiṣṭatarā nâite iti visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:26": " saced vayaṃ bhagavan nīcacittāś caṇḍālasadṛśacittā na viharema visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:27": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇâtmānam utkarṣayema paraṃ vā paṃsayema visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:28": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa vyāpādavigrahabhayād yojanaṃ vā yojanaśataṃ vā na palāyemêritāḥ samānā visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet",
    "T04sanss05u:29": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa śīlavantam ātmānaṃ pratijānīma bahuśrutaṃ vā dhutaguṇinaṃ vânyatarânyatareṇa vā guṇenâtmānam udbhāvayema visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:30": " saced vayaṃ bhagavann adyâgreṇa praticchannakalyāṇā vivṛtapāpā na viharema visaṃvādito 'smābhis tathāgato bhaved arhan samyaksaṃbuddhaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:31": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:32": " tatra bhagavān maitreyaṃ bodhisatvaṃ mahāsatvam āmantrayate sma /",
    "T04sanss05u:33": " karmâvaraṇaṃ maitreya",
    "T04sanss05u:34": " [ Bendall ed p99 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:35": " kṣapayitukāmena kulaputreṇa vā kuladuhitrā vâivaṃ samādānaṃ kartavyaṃ yathâibhiḥ kulaputraiḥ kṛtam iti //",
    "T04sanss05u:36": " sarvadharmâpravṛttinirdeśe 'py āha //",
    "T04sanss05u:37": " tṛṣkṛtva rātriṃ divasaṃ tathâiva /",
    "T04sanss05u:38": " sa bodhisatvān praṇameta mūrdhnā /",
    "T04sanss05u:39": " teṣāṃ na kiñcit skhalitaṃ gaveṣet /",
    "T04sanss05u:40": " careta caryāṃ hi sadā yathêṣṭam //",
    "T04sanss05u:41": " paśyed yadā kāmaguṇai ramantaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:42": " na tasya kiñcit skhalitaṃ gaveṣet /",
    "T04sanss05u:43": " guṇair anantāṃ vara bodhicaryāṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:44": " eṣo 'pi kālena hitāṃ spṛśeta //",
    "T04sanss05u:45": " yuktyânupūrvyā kriyayânupūrvyā /",
    "T04sanss05u:46": " bhavej jino nâiva hi ekavācā /",
    "T04sanss05u:47": " bahukalpakoṭyo niyutāni câiṣa /",
    "T04sanss05u:48": " sannāhasaṃprasthitanā-",
    "T04sanss05u:49": " [ Cambridge MS f55a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:50": " ny abhāvī //",
    "T04sanss05u:51": " atrâivâha /",
    "T04sanss05u:52": " ye kulaputrâivaṃrūpeṇa karmâvaraṇenânarthikāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:53": " tair na dvitīyasya bodhisatvasya sarvacaryāsu vipratipattavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:54": " sarvāḥ kriyās tasya vimoktavyāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:55": " evaṃ cittam utpādayitavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:56": " nâhaṃ paracittaṃ jāne durvijñeyā satvacaryā /",
    "T04sanss05u:57": " idaṃ ca khalu kulaputrârthavaśaṃ saṃpaśyaṃs tathāgatâivaṃ-",
    "T04sanss05u:58": " [ Bendall ed p100 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:59": " dharmaṃ deśayati /",
    "T04sanss05u:60": " na pudgalena pudgalaḥ pramātavyaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:61": " ahaṃ vā pudgalaṃ pramiṇuyāṃ yo vā syān mādṛśaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:62": " yaḥ kulaputrâtmānaṃ rakṣitukāmas tena na kasyacic caryā vivecayitavyā /",
    "T04sanss05u:63": " na pareṣāṃ vikuṭṭanā kartavyā /",
    "T04sanss05u:64": " ayam īdṛśo 'yam īdṛśêti /",
    "T04sanss05u:65": " buddhadharmâbhiyuktena bhavitavyaṃ rātriṃ divaṃ dharmapaliguddhamānasenêti //",
    "T04sanss05u:66": " tathā kṣitigarbhasūtre 'pi kathitaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:67": " atha tāvad eva bahūni śatasahasrāṇi vidvāṃsaḥ satvôtthāyâsanād yena bhagavāṃs tenâñjaliṃ praṇamyâivam āhuḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:68": " vayaṃ bhadanta bhagavataḥ puratâivaṃ praṇidhānaṃ kurmaḥ yāvac ciraṃ vayaṃ bhadanta bhagavan saṃsāre saṃsarema tāvan mātra pratilabdhakṣāntikāmā rājasthānaṃ pratilabhema /",
    "T04sanss05u:69": " mâmātyasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:70": " mā nagarajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:71": " mā grāmajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:72": " mā nigamajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:73": " mā purohitajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ mā bhaṭṭajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:74": " yāvan mā sârthavāhajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:75": " môpādhyāyajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:76": " mā śramaṇajyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:77": " mā gṛhapatijyeṣṭhasthānaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:78": " mā kuṭumbijyeṣṭhasthānaṃ yāvat sarvaśo vayaṃ mā satvānām adhipatisthānaṃ pratilabhema yāvan na kṣāntipratilabdhāḥ syāma /",
    "T04sanss05u:79": " yato nidānaṃ vayam evaṃrūpam atigāḍhaṃ karma buddhānāṃ śāsanam ākṣipema /",
    "T04sanss05u:80": " iti vistaraḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:81": " candrapradīpasūtre 'py anarthavivarjanam uktam /",
    "T04sanss05u:82": " nâsti pāpam akartavyaṃ kumārā teṣu bheṣyati /",
    "T04sanss05u:83": " mā tehi saṃsta-",
    "T04sanss05u:84": " [ Cambridge MS f55b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:85": " vaṃ sārddhaṃ kuryāḥ tvaṃ kāli paścime //",
    "T04sanss05u:86": " ālape saṃlapeyyāsi kuryāsī teṣv agauravaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:87": " ānālīnaḥ satkareyyāsy agrabodhayi kāraṇāt //",
    "T04sanss05u:88": " [ Bendall ed p101 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:89": " varṣâgraṃ paripṛcchitvā yas te vṛddhataro bhavet /",
    "T04sanss05u:90": " kuryāsi gauravaṃ tatra śirasā pādavandanaiḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:91": " na teṣāṃ skhalitaṃ paśyed bodhimaṇḍaṃ vipaśyatāṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:92": " pratighātaṃ na janayet maitracittaḥ sadā bhavet //",
    "T04sanss05u:93": " yady eṣāṃ skhalitaṃ paśyed doṣāṃs teṣāṃ na kīrtayet /",
    "T04sanss05u:94": " yādṛśaṃ kāhiti karma tādṛśaṃ lapsyate phalaṃ //",
    "T04sanss05u:95": " smitena mukhacandreṇa vṛddheṣu navakeṣu ca /",
    "T04sanss05u:96": " pūrvâbhāṣī bhaven nityaṃ hatamānaś ca sarvataḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:97": " cīvaraiḥ piṇḍapātaiś ca kuryāt teṣām anugrahaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:98": " evaṃ cittaṃ pradadhyās tvaṃ sarve bheṣyanti nāyakā /",
    "T04sanss05u:99": " iti //",
    "T04sanss05u:100": " yasya ca bodhicittôtpādike gauravaṃ prasādaś ca nôtpadyete /",
    "T04sanss05u:101": " tena svadurgatiprapātabhayarakṣârthaṃ dṛṣṭâdṛṣṭaprāmodyânubhavanârthaṃ svacittakaluṣaprasādanârthaṃ",
    "T04sanss05u:102": " cittakalyatācittakarmaṇyatāpratilābhârthaṃ ca yathâryagaṇḍavyūhe bodhicittôtpādikaguṇā",
    "T04sanss05u:103": " bhagavadāryamaitreyeṇâcāryasudhanam adhikṛtyôdbhāvitās tathā bhāvayitavyāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:104": " eṣa dṛṣṭva jaravyādhipīḍitān prāṇino duṣkhaśatair upadrutān /",
    "T04sanss05u:105": " janmamṛtyubhayaśokatāpitān teṣârthi carate krpâśayaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:106": " duṣkhayantraparipīḍitaṃ jagat dṛṣṭva pañcagaticakramaṇḍale /",
    "T04sanss05u:107": " jñānavajramayam eṣa te dṛḍhaṃ duṣkhayantragaticakrabhedanaṃ //",
    "T04sanss05u:108": " [ Bendall ed p102 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:109": " rāgadoṣatṛṇakhāṇukaṇṭakaṃ dṛṣṭisaṃgabahu kakṣasaṃkulam /",
    "T04sanss05u:110": " satvakṣetrapariśodhanârthikaḥ prajñalāṅgaladṛḍhaṃ gaveṣate //",
    "T04sanss05u:111": " mohavidyagahanâśayaṃ jagat prajñacakṣuhata naṣṭadaiśikaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:112": " tasya kṣema diśa-",
    "T04sanss05u:113": " [ Cambridge MS f56a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:114": " daiśikaḥ prabhuḥ sârthavāha jagato bhaviṣyati //",
    "T04sanss05u:115": " kṣāntidharmatrivimokṣavāhano jñānakhaḍga ripukleśadharṣakaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:116": " śūrasūtâbhayasya dāyako daiśako hi jagato bhaviṣyati //",
    "T04sanss05u:117": " dharmanāva samudānayaty ayaṃ jñānasāgarapathe suśikṣitaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:118": " śāntiratnavaradvīpanāyakaḥ karṇadhāra tribhavârṇave 'yam //",
    "T04sanss05u:119": " jñānaraśmipraṇidhānamaṇḍalaḥ sarvasatva bhavanâvabhāsakaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:120": " dharmadhātugagane samudgato buddhasūrya samudeśyate 'yam //",
    "T04sanss05u:121": " maitricandanasamādhiśītalaḥ sarvasatvasama cittasuprabhaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:122": " śukladharmaparipūrṇamaṇḍalo buddhacandra samudeśyate 'yam //",
    "T04sanss05u:123": " āśaye dṛḍhatale pratiṣṭhito bodhicaryânupūrvôdgataḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:124": " sarvadharmaratanâkaro hy ayaṃ jñānasāravaro bhaviṣyati //",
    "T04sanss05u:125": " bodhicittabhujagêndrasaṃbhavo dharmadhātugagane samudgataḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:126": " [ Bendall ed p103 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:127": " dharmameghayugapatpravarṣaṇaḥ sarvaśuklaphala śasyavardhanaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:128": " śuddhi vartti trimalattamo 'py ahaṃ maitrisneha smṛtibhājanaṃ dṛḍham /",
    "T04sanss05u:129": " bodhicittavimalâgnisuprabham dharmadīpa samujjvālayiṣyati //",
    "T04sanss05u:130": " bodhicittakalalaḥ kṛpârbudo maitrapeśir acalâśayo ghanaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:131": " bodhi aṅgam anupūrvasaṃbhavo buddhagarbhâyu saṃpravardhate //",
    "T04sanss05u:132": " puṇyagarbham abhivarddhayiṣyati prajñagarbham abhiśodhayiṣyati /",
    "T04sanss05u:133": " jñānagarbha samudeśyate 'yaṃ yādṛśaḥ praṇidhigarbhasaṃbhavaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:134": " īdṛśāḥ karuṇamaitradharmitāḥ satvamocana matī hitâśayāṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:135": " durlabhā jagi sdevamānuṣe yādṛśo 'yu viśuddhamānasaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:136": " īdṛśâśayasumūlasaṃsthito īdṛśo dṛḍhaprayogavarddhitaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:137": " īdṛśas tribhavachādanaprabho jñānavṛkṣaphaladaḥ sudurlabhaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:138": " eṣa sarvaguṇasaṃbhavârthikaḥ sarvadharmaparipṛ-",
    "T04sanss05u:139": " [ Cambridge MS f56b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:140": " cchanârthikaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:141": " sarvasaṃśayavidāraṇârthikaḥ sarvamitra bhajate 'tandritaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:142": " [ Bendall ed p104 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:143": " eṣa mārakalikleśasūdano eṣa dṛṣṭimalakleśaśodhanaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:144": " eṣa sarvajagamokṣaṇôdyato eṣa te sada viśeṣa paṇḍitaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:145": " eṣa durgati viśodhayiṣyati svargamārgam upadarśayiṣyati /",
    "T04sanss05u:146": " mokṣamārgam upaneṣyate jagad yādṛśe guṇapathe pratiṣṭhitaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:147": " eṣa sarvataduṣkhamocako /",
    "T04sanss05u:148": " eṣa sarvagatisaukhyadāyakaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:149": " eṣa sarvabhayapāśachedako /",
    "T04sanss05u:150": " bheṣyate bhagavatīnisūdana /",
    "T04sanss05u:151": " iti //",
    "T04sanss05u:152": " evam anayā bhāvanayânarthavivarjanaṃ sukaraṃ bhavati /",
    "T04sanss05u:153": " tathâdhyāśayasañcodanasūtre 'py anarthavivarjanam uktaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:154": " caturbhir maitreya dharmaiḥ samanvāgato bodhisatvayānikaḥ pudgalaḥ paścimāyāṃ pañcaśatyāṃ saddharmavipralope vartamāne 'kṣato 'nupahataḥ svastinā parimokṣyate //",
    "T04sanss05u:155": " katamaiś caturbhiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:156": " ātmaskhalitapratyavekṣaṇatayā /",
    "T04sanss05u:157": " pareṣāṃ bodhisatvayānikānāṃ pudgalānām āpattyacodanatayā /",
    "T04sanss05u:158": " mitrakulabhikṣād akulânavalokanatayā /",
    "T04sanss05u:159": " amanaskavacanaprativiramaṇatayā /",
    "T04sanss05u:160": " ebhir maitreya caturbhir iti pūrvavat //",
    "T04sanss05u:161": " aparaiś caturbhiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:162": " katamaiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:163": " alpaśrutasatvaparivarjanatayā /",
    "T04sanss05u:164": " parṣadanupādānatayā /",
    "T04sanss05u:165": " prāntaśayyâsananiṣevaṇatayā ca /",
    "T04sanss05u:166": " ātmadamaśamathayogam anuyuktatayā ca /",
    "T04sanss05u:167": " ebhiś caturbhir iti vistaraḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:168": " punar atrâivâha /",
    "T04sanss05u:169": " ādikarmikeṇa maitreya bodhisatvena prajñābalâdhānaprāptena lābhasatkāraparivarjitena lābhasatkāradoṣadarśinā bhavitavyaṃ //",
    "T04sanss05u:170": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:171": " saṃgaṇikârāmaparivarjitena saṃga-",
    "T04sanss05u:172": " [ Bendall ed p105 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:173": " ṇikârāmadoṣadarśinā bhavitavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:174": " bhāṣyârāmaparivarjitena bhāṣyârāmadoṣadarśi-",
    "T04sanss05u:175": " [ Cambridge MS f57a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:176": " nā bhavitavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:177": " nidrârāmavarjitena nidrârāmadoṣadarśinā bhavitavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:178": " karmârāmavarjitena karmârāmadoṣadarśinā bhavitavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:179": " prapañcârāmavarjitena prapañcârāmadoṣadarśinā bhavitavyaṃ //",
    "T04sanss05u:180": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:181": " iha maitreya bodhisatvena mahāsatvena rāgasaṃjanano lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:182": " smṛtividhvaṃsanakaro lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:183": " lābhâlābhatayônnāmâvanāmakaro lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:184": " mohôtpādano lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:185": " kulamātsaryâdhyavasāno lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:186": " ātmârthaniṣpādanatayā śāṭhyôtpādano lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:187": " caturāryavaṃśaparivarjanatayâhrīkyânapatrāpyasaṃjanano lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:188": " evaṃ sarvabuddhânanujñāno lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:189": " mānamadôtpādano lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:190": " gurūṇām avamānano lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:191": " mārapakṣo lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:192": " ekântapramādamūlaḥ kuśalamūlâpaharaṇo lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:193": " vidyuccakrâśanisadṛśo lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:194": " bahupaligodhapaliguddho mitrakulabhikṣād akulâvalokano daurmanasyasaṃjananaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:195": " buddhivibhrāmaṇo lābhasatkāraḥ priyavastupariṇāmanatayā śokabhājano lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:196": " catuḥsmṛtyupasthānasaṃmoṣaṇaḥ śukladharmadurbalīkaraṇaḥ catuḥsamyakprahāṇaparihāṇakaraṇo lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:197": " ṛddhyabhijñāparihāṇakaraṇaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:198": " pūrvaṃ satkārapaścād asatkārakaraṇaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:199": " amitrasatkaraṇamitraprahāṇo lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:200": " parâbhisaṃdhānatayā gaṇikāsadṛśaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:201": " dhyana-",
    "T04sanss05u:202": " [ Cambridge MS f57b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:203": " apramāṇaparivarjanaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:204": " narakatiryagyoniyamalokaprapātano lābhasatkāraḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:205": " devadattôdrakasamācāro lābhasatkāraḥ pratyavekṣitavyaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:206": " [ Bendall ed p106 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:207": " ime evaṃrūpā maitreya lābhasatkāre ādīnavā ye bodhisatvena pratyavekṣitavyāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:208": " pratyavekṣya câlpêcchatāyāṃ rantavyaṃ na paritaptavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:209": " tat kasya hetoḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:210": " alpêcchasya hi maitreyêmae evaṃrūpā doṣā na bhavanti na câsyântarāyā bhavanti buddhadharmāṇāṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:211": " anirviṇṇaś ca bhavati gṛhipravrajitebhyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:212": " anurakṣaṇīyaś ca bhavati devamanuṣyāṇāṃ pariśuddhâśayasthitaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:213": " asaṃtrastaś ca bhavati sarvadurgatinipātebhyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:214": " anabhibhūtaś ca bhavati tarjanāvigataḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:215": " asaṃhāryaś ca bhavati māraviṣayavimuktaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:216": " adharṣaṇīyaś ca bhavati sarvavyasanaiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:217": " abhilaṣaṇīyaś ca bhavati devamanuṣyāṇāṃ dhyānâbhyāsâvasthitaḥ [[DOUBT]] /",
    "T04sanss05u:218": " spaṣṭaś ca bhavati māyāśāṭhyaprahīṇo 'pramattaś ca bhavati pañcakāmaguṇadoṣadarśī yathāvādī tathākārī bhavaty āryavaṃśe sthitaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:219": " abhilaṣitaś ca bhavati vidvadbhiḥ sabrahmacāribhiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:220": " imāṃ maitreyâivaṃrūpām anuśaṃsāṃ viditvā paṇḍitena bodhisatvenâdhyāśayenâlpêcchatāyāṃ rantavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:221": " alpêcchatâsevitavyā sarvalābhasatkaraprahāṇāyêti //",
    "T04sanss05u:222": " saṃgaṇikām adhikṛtyâha /",
    "T04sanss05u:223": " vijahya rāgaṃ vijahya doṣaṃ na tiṣṭhate saṃgaṇikāsu yogī /",
    "T04sanss05u:224": " bhavaty asau tatpravaṇas tannimnaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:225": " etena doṣeṇa ratiṃ na kuryāt /",
    "T04sanss05u:226": " auddhatya hāsyaṃ ca tathā vitarkā /",
    "T04sanss05u:227": " bhavanty amī saṃgaṇikāsu sarve //",
    "T04sanss05u:228": " saṃkīrṇacārī hi bhavaty asaṃvṛtaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:229": " karoti yaḥ saṃgaṇikām asārām //",
    "T04sanss05u:230": " lokasya mantreṣu ramanti bālā /",
    "T04sanss05u:231": " hīyanti cêhâgrakathāsu bālāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:232": " [ Bendall ed p107 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:233": " pradoṣa vardhenti vitarkôtsadā /",
    "T04sanss05u:234": " etena doṣeṇa na tatra rājate //",
    "T04sanss05u:235": " na vardhate câpi śrutena bhikṣuḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:236": " ayuktamantreṣu ratiṃ janitvā /",
    "T04sanss05u:237": " tasmāt",
    "T04sanss05u:238": " [ Cambridge MS f57b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:239": " parityajyâyuktamantrān /",
    "T04sanss05u:240": " dharme ratiṃ vindatha nityakālam //",
    "T04sanss05u:241": " sahasraśo 'ṣṭhāni mayā svakāni /",
    "T04sanss05u:242": " tyaktāni bodhiṃ pratikāṅkṣa tarhi /",
    "T04sanss05u:243": " na câsmi tṛptaḥ śṛṇumāna dharmaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:244": " te khedam eṣyanti śṛṇonta dharmam //",
    "T04sanss05u:245": " sarveṇa sarvaṃ parivarjanīyā /",
    "T04sanss05u:246": " ayuktamantrāś câśiṣṭamantrāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:247": " dharme vare tatra ratiṃ janetha /",
    "T04sanss05u:248": " yo durlabhaḥ kalpaśatair anekaiḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:249": " vane vasantena guṇârthikena /",
    "T04sanss05u:250": " parasya doṣā na hi vīkṣitavyāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:251": " ahaṃ viśiṣṭo 'ham eva śreṣṭho /",
    "T04sanss05u:252": " nâiva cittaṃ samupādanīyam //",
    "T04sanss05u:253": " [ Bendall ed p108 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:254": " mado 'yaṃ sarvapramādamūlo /",
    "T04sanss05u:255": " na hīnabhikṣū avamanyitavyāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:256": " anupūrvâiṣo iha śāsanasya /",
    "T04sanss05u:257": " nâikena janmena labhate bodhim //",
    "T04sanss05u:258": " atrêva bhāṣyârāmam adhikṛtyâha /",
    "T04sanss05u:259": " agauravo bhoti śrutena matto /",
    "T04sanss05u:260": " vivādamantreṣu niviṣṭa bhoti /",
    "T04sanss05u:261": " muṣitaśrutiś câpi asaṃprajanyo /",
    "T04sanss05u:262": " bhāṣye ramantasya",
    "T04sanss05u:263": " [ Cambridge MS f58b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:264": " ime hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:265": " adhyātmacintâtta [[DOUBT]] sudūra bhotī /",
    "T04sanss05u:266": " cittaṃ na kāyaś ca prasanna bhoti /",
    "T04sanss05u:267": " unnāmanāmāni bahūni gacchatī /",
    "T04sanss05u:268": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:269": " saddharmacittāt tu praṇaṣṭu bālāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:270": " sukarkaśo bhoti asnigdhacittaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:271": " vipaśyanāyāḥ śamathāc ca dūre /",
    "T04sanss05u:272": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:273": " agauravo bhoti sadā gurūṇāṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:274": " [ Bendall ed p109 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:275": " paligodhamantreṣu ratiṃ janitvā /",
    "T04sanss05u:276": " asārasthāyī parihīṇaprajño /",
    "T04sanss05u:277": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:278": " amānito devaguṇaiḥ sa bhoti /",
    "T04sanss05u:279": " nâpy asya tasmin spṛha saṃjananti /",
    "T04sanss05u:280": " pratisaṃvidāto bhavatī vihīno /",
    "T04sanss05u:281": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:282": " paribhāṣyate câpi sa paṇḍitebhiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:283": " ye kacid astī pṛthakāyasākṣī [[DOUBT]] /",
    "T04sanss05u:284": " nirarthakaṃ jīvitu tasya bhotī /",
    "T04sanss05u:285": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:286": " sa śocate kālu karotu bālaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:287": " pratipatti hīno 'smi kim adya kuryāṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:288": " suduṣkhito bhoti alabdhagādho /",
    "T04sanss05u:289": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:290": " calâcalo bhoti tṛṇaṃ yathêritaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:291": " vicikitsate evam asau na saṃśayaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:292": " na tasya jātū dṛḍha buddhi bhotī /",
    "T04sanss05u:293": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:294": " [ Bendall ed p110 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:295": " naṭā yathā tiṣṭhati raṅgamadhye /",
    "T04sanss05u:296": " anyāna śūrāṇa guṇān prabhāṣate /",
    "T04sanss05u:297": " svayaṃ ca bhotī pratipattihīno /",
    "T04sanss05u:298": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:299": " śaṭhaś ca so bhoti laghunirāśaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:300": " punaḥ punaś cârabhate vivādam /",
    "T04sanss05u:301": " so dūrato āryadharmasya bhotī /",
    "T04sanss05u:302": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:303": " saṃhṛṣyate satkrṭâlpasthāmaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:304": " prakampate viprakṛto 'jānī /",
    "T04sanss05u:305": " kapir yathā cañcalacitta bhotī /",
    "T04sanss05u:306": " bhāṣye ramantasyême hi doṣāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:307": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:308": " ramitva bhāṣyasmi ciraṃ pi kālaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:309": " na vindate prītim ihâtmasaukhyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:310": " varaṃ hi ekasya padasya cintanā /",
    "T04sanss05u:311": " prītiṃ pade yatra labhed anantam //",
    "T04sanss05u:312": " nêkṣutvace sāram ihâsti kiñcin /",
    "T04sanss05u:313": " madhye 'sti tatsāra supremaṇīyaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:314": " bhuktvā tvacaṃ nêha punaḥ saśakyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:315": " labdhuṃ nareṇêkṣurasaṃ pradhānam //",
    "T04sanss05u:316": " [ Bendall ed p111 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:317": " yathā tvacaṃ tadvad avaihi bhāṣyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:318": " yathā rasas tadvad ihârthacintā [[DOUBT]] /",
    "T04sanss05u:319": " tasmād dhi bhāṣye tu ratiṃ vihāya /",
    "T04sanss05u:320": " cintethârthaṃ sadâpramattāḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:321": " nidrârāmam adhikṛtyâha /",
    "T04sanss05u:322": " mahac ca so vardhati mohajālaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:323": " vicikitsako bhoti sa dṛṣṭiprāptaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:324": " dṛṣṭīkṛtāny asya bahūni bhontī /",
    "T04sanss05u:325": " yasmāna middhe 'bhiratiṃ prayāti //",
    "T04sanss05u:326": " prajñā ca teṣāṃ bhavatī sudurbalā /",
    "T04sanss05u:327": " parihīyate buddhi na tasya bhoti /",
    "T04sanss05u:328": " jñānāc ca so hīyati nityakālaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:329": " yasmāna middhe 'bhiratiṃ prayāti //",
    "T04sanss05u:330": " kusīdâjño 'laso 'prajño 'manuṣyâvatāra labhenti tasya /",
    "T04sanss05u:331": " viheṭhayante ca vane vasantaṃ yasmāna middhe 'bhiratiṃ prayāti //",
    "T04sanss05u:332": " kuśalena cittena sadânarthiko /",
    "T04sanss05u:333": " dharme ca chando na hi bhoti tasya /",
    "T04sanss05u:334": " adharmakāyaś ca sa bhoti bhūyo yasmāna middhe 'bhiratiṃ prayāti //",
    "T04sanss05u:335": " saddharmachandena vihīnamūḍhaḥ parihoyate sarvaguṇehi bā-",
    "T04sanss05u:336": " [ Cambridge MS f59a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:337": " laḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:338": " śuklaṃ ca ghāteti tamo 'dhigacchatī /",
    "T04sanss05u:339": " [ Bendall ed p112 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:340": " yasmāna middhe 'bhiratiṃ prayāti //",
    "T04sanss05u:341": " aviśārado bhoti pralīnacittaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:342": " prāmodya tasyô bhavatī na nityaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:343": " nidrayâpagrastaḥ śithilâṅga bhotī /",
    "T04sanss05u:344": " yasmāna middhe 'bhiratiṃ prayāti //",
    "T04sanss05u:345": " ātmā tu jñātvā ca kusīdaprāptaḥ īrṣyāyate vīryabalair upetān /",
    "T04sanss05u:346": " vīryânvitānāṃ câvarṇa bhāṣate yasmāna middhe 'bhiratiṃ prayāti //",
    "T04sanss05u:347": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:348": " yat sarvaduṣkhasya tamasya nāśanaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:349": " apāyaparivarjanatayā mūlaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:350": " sarvehi buddhair hi sadā praśastaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:351": " taṃ vīryam āryaṃ satataṃ bhajasva //",
    "T04sanss05u:352": " karmârāmam adhikṛtyâha //",
    "T04sanss05u:353": " sudurvaco bhoti gurūbhi coditaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:354": " pradakṣiṇaṃ gṛhṇati nânuśāsanaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:355": " vipannaśīlaś ca sa bhoti kṣipraṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:356": " doṣâmī karmarate bhavanti //",
    "T04sanss05u:357": " utkaṇṭhito bhoti sa nityakālaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:358": " gṛhasthakarmāṇi sadā vicintayan /",
    "T04sanss05u:359": " dhyānaprahāṇaiś ca na tasya kṛtyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:360": " doṣâmī karmarate bhavati //",
    "T04sanss05u:361": " tīvraś ca saṃjāyati tasya rāgo /",
    "T04sanss05u:362": " rasâraseṣu grasitaḥ sa mūrcchitaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:363": " [ Bendall ed p113 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:364": " na tuṣyate 'sāv itarêtareṇa /",
    "T04sanss05u:365": " doṣâmī karmarate bhavanti //",
    "T04sanss05u:366": " mahatyā ca bhotī pariṣāya tuṣṭho /",
    "T04sanss05u:367": " sa duṣkhito bhoti tayā vihīnaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:368": " saṃkīrṇa bhotī sayathêha gardabho /",
    "T04sanss05u:369": " doṣâmī karmarate bhavanti //",
    "T04sanss05u:370": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:371": " divā ca rātrau cânanyacitto /",
    "T04sanss05u:372": " bhakte ca coḍe ca bhavaty abhīkṣṇaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:373": " svanarthiko bhoti guṇaiḥ sa sarvadā /",
    "T04sanss05u:374": " doṣâmī karmarate bhavanti //",
    "T04sanss05u:375": " kṛtyāny asau pṛcchati laukikāni /",
    "T04sanss05u:376": " ayuktamantraiś ca ratiṃ prayāti /",
    "T04sanss05u:377": " yuktaiś ca mantraiḥ sa na vindate ratiṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:378": " doṣâmī karmarate bhavanti //",
    "T04sanss05u:379": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:380": " atha khalu maitreyo bodhisatvo mahāsatvo bhagavantam etad avocat /",
    "T04sanss05u:381": " suparīttaprajñās te bhagavan bodhisatvā bhaviṣyanti vihīnaprajñā ye 'gradharmān varjayitvā hīnāni karmāṇy ārapsyante //",
    "T04sanss05u:382": " evam ukte bhagavān maitreyaṃ bodhisatvaṃ mahāsatvam etad avocat /",
    "T04sanss05u:383": " evam etan maitreya /",
    "T04sanss05u:384": " evam etad yathā vadasi",
    "T04sanss05u:385": " [ Cambridge MS f59b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:386": " suparīttaprajñās te bodhisatvā bhaviṣyanti ye 'gradharmān parivarjayitvā hīnāni karmāṇy ārapsyante /",
    "T04sanss05u:387": " api tv ārocayāmi te maitreya prativedayāmi te /",
    "T04sanss05u:388": " na te bodhisatvās tathāgata-",
    "T04sanss05u:389": " [ Bendall ed p114 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:390": " śāsane pravrajitā yeṣāṃ nâsti yogo nâsti dhyānaṃ nâsti prahāṇaṃ nâsty adhyayanaṃ nâsti bāhuśrutyaparyeṣṭiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:391": " api tu maitreya dhyānaprahāṇaprabhāvitaṃ tathāgataśāsanaṃ jñānasaṃskṛtaṃ jñānasamāhitaṃ abhiyogaprabhāvitaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:392": " na gṛhikarmântavaiyāpṛtyaprabhāvitaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:393": " ayuktayogānām etat karma saṃsārâbhiratānāṃ yad uta vaiyāpṛtyaṃ laukikakṛtyapaligodhaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:394": " na tatra bodhisatvena spṛhôtpādayitavyā /",
    "T04sanss05u:395": " sacen maitreya vaiyāpṛtyâbhirato bodhisatvaḥ saptaratnamayaiḥ stūpair imaṃ trisāhasramahāsāhasraṃ lokadhātuṃ pūrayet /",
    "T04sanss05u:396": " nâhaṃ tenârādhito bhaveyaṃ na mānito nâpi satkṛtaḥ // pe /",
    "T04sanss05u:397": " tatra jambūdvīpaḥ pūritaḥ syād vaiyāpṛtyakarair bodhisatvaiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:398": " sarvais tair ekasyôddeśasvâdhyāyâbhiyuktasya bodhisatvasyôpasthānaparicaryā karaṇīyā /",
    "T04sanss05u:399": " jambūdvīpapramāṇaiś côddeśasvâdhyāyâbhiyuktair bodhisatvair ekasya pratisaṃlayanâbhiyuktasya bodhisatvasyôpasthānaparicaryā kartavyā //",
    "T04sanss05u:400": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:401": " tat kasya hetoḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:402": " duṣkaram etat karma yad uta prajñākarma /",
    "T04sanss05u:403": " uttaraṃ niruttaraṃ sarvatrailokyaprativiśiṣṭam abhyudgataṃ tasmāt tarhi maitreya bodhisatvena yogârthikena vīryam ārabdhukāmena prajñāyām abhiyoktavyam iti //",
    "T04sanss05u:404": " prapañcârāmam adhikṛtyâha /",
    "T04sanss05u:405": " aṣṭâkṣaṇā tasya na bhonti dūre /",
    "T04sanss05u:406": " kṣaṇasaṃpadā tasya na bhoti śreṣṭhā /",
    "T04sanss05u:407": " ete 'narthā sya bhavanti nityaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:408": " doṣâmī tasya prapañcacāriṇaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:409": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:410": " doṣān imān samyag avetya paṇḍitaḥ sarvān prapañcān parivarjīta /",
    "T04sanss05u:411": " sulabhânarthā hi prapa-",
    "T04sanss05u:412": " [ Cambridge MS f60a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:413": " ñcacāriṇaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:414": " tasmāt prapañcena na saṃvaseta //",
    "T04sanss05u:415": " [ Bendall ed p115 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:416": " yāyāc chataṃ yojanakaṃ paraṃ varaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:417": " yatra prapañco stiya vigraho vā /",
    "T04sanss05u:418": " na tatra vāsaṃ na niketu kuryān muhūrttamātraṃ stiya yatra kleśaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:419": " nârthârthikāḥ pravrajitā guṇârthikā /",
    "T04sanss05u:420": " mā vigraha kurvatha dustacittāḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:421": " na vo 'sti kṣetraṃ na kṛṣir vaṇijyā /",
    "T04sanss05u:422": " syur yasyârthāya prapañcâite //",
    "T04sanss05u:423": " na putra dhītā na ca vo 'sti bhāryā /",
    "T04sanss05u:424": " na câsya mitraṃ na ca bandhuvargaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:425": " dāsyo na dāsā na cêśvaratvaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:426": " mā vigrahaṃ kurvatha pravrajitvā //",
    "T04sanss05u:427": " kāṣāyavastrāṇi gṛhītva śraddhayā /",
    "T04sanss05u:428": " śāntapraśāntair hi niṣevitāni /",
    "T04sanss05u:429": " śāntapraśāntôpaśānta bhotha /",
    "T04sanss05u:430": " prapañca varjitva janetha kṣāntim //",
    "T04sanss05u:431": " āśīviṣān rakṣatha raudracittān /",
    "T04sanss05u:432": " narakāś ca tiryag viṣayo yamasya /",
    "T04sanss05u:433": " prapañcacārasya na bhonti dūre /",
    "T04sanss05u:434": " tasmād dhi kṣāntau janayeta vīryam //",
    "T04sanss05u:435": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:436": " imena yogena labheta śuddhiṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:437": " kṣapayitva karmâvaraṇaṃ aśeṣaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:438": " dharṣeti māraṃ sacalaṃ savāhanaṃ yo dhīru tasyâiva janeti kṣāntim /",
    "T04sanss05u:439": " iti //",
    "T04sanss05u:440": " [ Bendall ed p116 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:441": " saṃkṣepatas tatrânarthavivarjanam uktaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:442": " tasmāt tarhi maitreya bodhisatvayānikena kulaputreṇa vā kuladuhitrā vā paścimāyāṃ",
    "T04sanss05u:443": " pañcaśatyāṃ saddharmapralope vartamāne 'kṣatanânupahatena svastinā parimoktukāmena",
    "T04sanss05u:444": " sarvakarmâvaraṇāni kṣapayitukāmenâsaṃsargâbhiratena bhavitavyam araṇyavanaprāntavāsinânabhiyuktasatva",
    "T04sanss05u:445": " parivarjitenâtmaskhalitagaveṣiṇā paraskhalitâgaveṣiṇā tuṣṇībhāvâbhiratena prajñāpāramitāvihārâbhiratenêti //",
    "T04sanss05u:446": " āryaratnameghe 'py anarthavarjanam uktaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:447": " tāvat piṇḍāya carati yāvad asya kāryasya prāptir bhavati /",
    "T04sanss05u:448": " anyatra yeṣu sthāneṣu caṇḍā vā kukkurās taruṇavatsā vā gāvaḥ prakṛtiduḥśīlā vā tiryagyonigatā /",
    "T04sanss05u:449": " viheṭhanâbhiprāyā vā strīpuruṣadārakadārikā jugupsi-",
    "T04sanss05u:450": " [ Cambridge MS f60b ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:451": " tāni vā sthānāni /",
    "T04sanss05u:452": " tāni sarveṇa sarvaṃ varjayatîti //",
    "T04sanss05u:453": " anenâitad darśitaṃ bhavati yad dṛṣṭe 'pi bādhākarâivaṃvidhe /",
    "T04sanss05u:454": " tad avarjayatâpattir bhavatîti //",
    "T04sanss05u:455": " atha yad evamādy anarthavarjanam uktaṃ kenâital labhyate sarvaniṣphalasyandavarjanāt /",
    "T04sanss05u:456": " phalam atra parârthaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:457": " tadarthaṃ yaḥ syando na saṃvartate /",
    "T04sanss05u:458": " sa niṣphalatvād varjayitavyaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:459": " yathā candrapradīpasūtre kāyasaṃvaramadhye paṭhyate /",
    "T04sanss05u:460": " na hastalolupo bhavati na pādalolupaḥ hastapādasaṃyatêti //",
    "T04sanss05u:461": " tathā daśadharmakasūtre 'pi deśitaṃ hastavikṣepaḥ pādavikṣepo 'dhāvanaṃ paridhāvanaṃ laṅghanaṃ plavanam idam ucyate kāyadauṣṭhulyam iti //",
    "T04sanss05u:462": " [ Bendall ed p117 ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:463": " āryadharmasaṃgītisūtre tu yathā bodhisatvānāṃ parârthād anyat karma na kalpate /",
    "T04sanss05u:464": " tathā spaṣṭam eva paridīpitaṃ yat kiñcid bhagavan bodhisatvānāṃ kāyakarma yat kiñcid",
    "T04sanss05u:465": " vākkarma yat kiñcin manaskarma tat sarvaṃ satvâvekṣitaṃ pravartate mahākaruṇâdhipateyaṃ",
    "T04sanss05u:466": " satvahitâdhiṣṭhānanimittaṃ sarvasatvahitasukhâdhyāśayapravṛttaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:467": " sâivaṃ hitâśayaḥ evaṃ saṃjñībhavati /",
    "T04sanss05u:468": " sa mayā pratipattiḥ pratipattavyayā sarvasatvānāṃ hitâvahā sukhâvahā ca //",
    "T04sanss05u:469": " pe //",
    "T04sanss05u:470": " āyataneṣu śūnyagrāmavat pratyavekṣaṇā pratipattiḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:471": " na câyatanaparityāgaṃ spṛhayatîti //",
    "T04sanss05u:472": " āryagaganagañjasūtre 'py uktaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:473": " tad yathâpi nāma chidrān mārutaḥ praviśati /",
    "T04sanss05u:474": " evam eva yato yatâiva cittasya chidraṃ bhavati tatas tatâiva māro 'vatāraṃ labhate /",
    "T04sanss05u:475": " tasmāt sadâchidracittena bodhisatvena bhavitavyaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:476": " tatrêyam achidracittatā yad idaṃ sarvâkārajñatāyāḥ śūnyatāyāḥ paripūrir iti //",
    "T04sanss05u:477": " kā punar iyaṃ sarvâkāravarôpetā śūnyatā /",
    "T04sanss05u:478": " yêyaṃ bodhisatvacaryāyâparityāgenâbhyasyamānā /",
    "T04sanss05u:479": " abhyastā vā /",
    "T04sanss05u:480": " sarvabhāvaśūnyatā /",
    "T04sanss05u:481": " eṣā ca ratnacūḍasūtre vistareṇâkhyātā //",
    "T04sanss05u:482": " tathâkṣayamatisūtre 'pi darśitaṃ /",
    "T04sanss05u:483": " pāpakā-",
    "T04sanss05u:484": " [ Cambridge MS f61a ---> ]",
    "T04sanss05u:485": " nām akuśalānāṃ dharmāṇāṃ prahāṇāya chandaṃ janayatîty atra prastāve yāni cânyāni punaḥ kānicid anyāny api cittavikṣepakarāṇi yāni samādhiskandhasya vipakṣāya saṃvartante /",
    "T04sanss05u:486": " ayam ucyate samādhivipakṣaḥ /",
    "T04sanss05u:487": " yāvad ime ucyante pāpakâkuśalā dharmêti //",
    "T04sanss05u:488": " śikṣāsamuccaye śīlapāramitāyām anarthavivarjanaṃ pañcamaḥ paricchedaḥ //",
    "T04sanss05u:489": " Copyright (c) 2002 by Jens Braarvig - Oslo"
}